DOCKERIZED EXPRESS

  A dockerized Express application generator.

BUILD IMAGE

  make

  or

  make build

INSTALL EXECUTABLE

  make install

USAGE

  First, add these lines to your .bashrc to ensure ~/bin is in your PATH:

    if ! echo "${PATH}" | grep -Eq "(^|:)${HOME}/bin(:|$)"; then
      export PATH=${HOME}/bin:${PATH}
    fi

  Then...

    express app_name

UNINSTALL EXECUTABLE

  make uninstall
